  <section class="section">
    <h2>Why <span class="underline-aq">Biofloc</span></h2>
    <p>
      Our biofloc-based aquaculture systems are engineered to deliver consistent, commercial-scale production while maintaining strict control over water quality and animal health. By operating in a closed, monitored environment, we significantly reduce exposure to external contamination, seasonal variability, and disease outbreaks common in traditional pond-based systems.
    </p>
		<p>
			Biofloc technology enables minimal water exchange, allowing beneficial microbial communities to recycle waste nutrients directly within the system. This results in improved feed conversion ratios, more stable growth rates, and reduced dependency on external water sources — a key advantage in regions where water efficiency and biosecurity are critical.
		</p>
